---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <section id="hero" class="pt-40">
      <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-12">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-heading font-light mb-8">
          Warranty Policy
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-base md:text-lg max-w-xl mb-24 font-normal font-heading uppercase text-black/80"
        >
          COMPREHENSIVE WARRANTY COVERAGE FOR ALL CAN SIGNAGE PRODUCTS
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="warranty-content" class="pb-10 pt-20 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Warranty Policy</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-gray-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Non-Refundable Services</h3>
          <p>
            All payments for subscriptions, IQ World software, and CANSIGNAGE displays are non-refundable. 
            Refunds will not be provided after a purchase is completed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Terms and Conditions</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
          During the warranty period, CANSIGNAGE will provide free repair services for our products 
          according to the conditions outlined below.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Warranty Coverage</h3>
        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">
            We offer a <strong>1-year warranty</strong> for all our products, starting from the activation date.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What's NOT Covered Under Warranty</h3>
        
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Damaged Products</h4>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Damage sustained during transportation, relocation, or installation site modification</li>
          <li>• Defective products resulting from incorrect customer installation or deviation from owner's manual and CANSIGNAGE instructions</li>
          <li>• Products installed in unsuitable environments (high dust, oil mist, chemical substances, extreme temperatures, or high humidity)</li>
          <li>• Damage from abuse, neglect, carelessness, incorrect maintenance or storage, acts of God, or circumstances beyond CANSIGNAGE's control</li>
          <li>• External damage including water damage, power surges, lightning strikes, and power outages</li>
          <li>• Display, open box, discounted, or refurbished goods with missing or damaged parts</li>
          <li>• Damage caused by viruses, Trojan horses, worms, bugs, or other malicious software</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Product Issues</h4>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Problems caused by poor signal reception or incorrect setup</li>
          <li>• Issues from using non-CANSIGNAGE recommended accessories, software, or parts</li>
          <li>• Problems resulting from product modifications</li>
          <li>• Issues from repairs or replacements by unauthorized service centers</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Additional Exclusions</h4>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Consumable components or add-ons (such as fuses or disposable batteries)</li>
          <li>• Products with altered, vandalized, or removed original manufacturing serial numbers</li>
          <li>• Image retention or sticking from displaying static images or patterns</li>
          <li>• Display panel life calculated when lamp brightness exceeds 50% of original value</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Software Usage Responsibilities</h3>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-800">Customer Obligations:</h4>
          <ol class="space-y-2 text-blue-700">
            <li>1. Comply with all technological restrictions on software usage</li>
            <li>2. <strong>Prohibited activities:</strong>
              <ul class="ml-4 mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li>i) Circumventing technological restrictions in the software</li>
                <li>ii) Reverse engineering, decompiling, or disassembling the program</li>
                <li>iii) Duplicating software beyond agreed amounts</li>
                <li>iv) Making software publicly available for replication</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>3. Software warranty does not cover defects from improper modifications, abuse, misuse, or non-intended usage</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mt-8">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-yellow-800">Important Notice</h4>
          <p class="text-yellow-700">
            Items not covered by warranty will incur appropriate additional fees for repair or replacement services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Need Support?</h4>
          <p>
            For warranty claims or questions, contact us at 
            <a href="mailto:sales@cansignage.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">sales@cansignage.com</a> 
            or call <strong>+91 91523 98498</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>